# CODEOWNERS — automatic PR reviewer assignment.
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Order matters: the LAST matching pattern wins for a given file.
# A single approval from ANY listed owner for a touched path satisfies
# the branch-protection "require review from code owners" rule.
#
# Policy: both Allen and Ronan are owners of every path. GitHub's
# auto-request will nominate the SUBJECT-MATTER LEAD listed first for
# each area, but either contributor can approve any PR. This keeps the
# tender push unblocked if one person is unavailable.

# Default owners — everything not matched below.
*                                   @allenwixted @ronanwalsh

